=Episode 14=

11
00:00:46,220 --> 00:00:47,300
Qian Cheng!

12
00:00:52,980 --> 00:00:54,260
What should I do?

13
00:00:54,700 --> 00:00:56,340
My family declared bankruptcy.

14
00:00:56,860 --> 00:00:57,780
My dad said

15
00:00:58,020 --> 00:01:00,500
I offended someone I shouldn't.

16
00:01:01,180 --> 00:01:02,660
Qian Cheng,

17
00:01:02,660 --> 00:01:03,420
I have nowhere to go.

18
00:01:03,420 --> 00:01:04,020
So?

19
00:01:04,500 --> 00:01:05,380
Why are you here?

20
00:01:07,500 --> 00:01:09,100
I have nowhere to go now.

21
00:01:09,100 --> 00:01:10,700
Qian Cheng, what should I do?

22
00:01:12,300 --> 00:01:13,020
I'm sorry,

23
00:01:13,460 --> 00:01:14,100
Ms. Lin.

24
00:01:14,380 --> 00:01:15,220
I barely know you.

25
00:01:15,820 --> 00:01:16,820
I am under no obligation

26
00:01:16,820 --> 00:01:18,140
to provide you with accommodation.

27
00:01:20,900 --> 00:01:21,540
Barely know me?

28
00:01:24,300 --> 00:01:25,020
Qian Cheng,

29
00:01:26,700 --> 00:01:27,940
don't be too outrageous.

30
00:01:29,260 --> 00:01:30,380
How much money have I spent on you,

31
00:01:30,380 --> 00:01:31,220
how many gifts have I given you,

32
00:01:31,220 --> 00:01:32,180
and you've forgotten them all?

33
00:01:32,900 --> 00:01:34,260
We simply take what we need.

34
00:01:34,700 --> 00:01:35,860
Didn't you get a lot

35
00:01:36,140 --> 00:01:37,420
from me too?

36
00:01:38,020 --> 00:01:39,860
Not to mention a perfect boyfriend.

37
00:01:42,740 --> 00:01:43,380
You're shameless.

38
00:01:46,700 --> 00:01:47,380
Lin Miaomiao,

39
00:01:48,060 --> 00:01:49,140
for me, Qian Cheng,

40
00:01:49,580 --> 00:01:50,500
a worthless person

41
00:01:50,900 --> 00:01:52,260
is no different from a dog.

42
00:01:52,620 --> 00:01:53,260
Remember,

43
00:01:53,820 --> 00:01:55,380
don't look for me again.

44
00:01:58,700 --> 00:01:59,700
Qian Cheng,

45
00:01:59,900 --> 00:02:01,380
you jerk!

46
00:02:06,260 --> 00:02:06,740
Bai Yu,

47
00:02:07,100 --> 00:02:08,380
about Lin Miaomiao...

48
00:02:09,100 --> 00:02:09,980
I'm sorry, Your Highness.

49
00:02:10,580 --> 00:02:11,540
I had to do that.

50
00:02:11,940 --> 00:02:13,060
I couldn't take it anymore.

51
00:02:14,500 --> 00:02:15,940
Did I say you did something wrong?

52
00:02:17,340 --> 00:02:18,620
What goes around

53
00:02:18,860 --> 00:02:20,260
comes around.

54
00:02:20,580 --> 00:02:23,020
I was more vicious back then than you.

55
00:02:23,980 --> 00:02:25,500
It's just that if this matter

56
00:02:25,980 --> 00:02:28,140
gets to Mrs. Bai,

57
00:02:28,940 --> 00:02:30,260
I'm afraid she will say

58
00:02:30,260 --> 00:02:31,940
that I'm somewhat spoiled.

59
00:02:32,660 --> 00:02:33,500
Don't worry.

60
00:02:34,100 --> 00:02:35,580
Although Grandma
is prejudiced against you,

61
00:02:35,580 --> 00:02:36,220
it is unlikely...

62
00:02:36,220 --> 00:02:37,100
Unlikely what?

63
00:02:45,860 --> 00:02:46,820
Well,

64
00:02:47,180 --> 00:02:48,580
not only am I somewhat spoiled,

65
00:02:49,100 --> 00:02:50,500
but I'm also vicious

66
00:02:50,500 --> 00:02:51,540
and vengeful.

67
00:02:52,340 --> 00:02:54,100
Anyone who dares hurt me

68
00:02:54,100 --> 00:02:55,700
must pay the price.

69
00:02:56,740 --> 00:02:57,460
Mr. Bai,

70
00:02:58,100 --> 00:02:58,780
are you afraid?

71
00:02:59,340 --> 00:02:59,980
Not at all.

72
00:03:01,340 --> 00:03:02,340
I'm not afraid of anything

73
00:03:03,460 --> 00:03:04,540
except losing you.

74
00:03:06,940 --> 00:03:10,180
