75
00:03:10,180 --> 00:03:13,460
♪To play hide and seek with you♪

76
00:03:13,460 --> 00:03:16,900
♪Found by you, fell into your arms♪

77
00:03:16,900 --> 00:03:19,660
♪Your smile lights up my whole world♪

78
00:03:20,460 --> 00:03:21,180
Li,

79
00:03:21,740 --> 00:03:24,100
do you smell anything?

80
00:03:26,780 --> 00:03:27,740
What do you smell?

81
00:03:28,260 --> 00:03:29,500
The stinky smell of love.

82
00:03:30,340 --> 00:03:31,580
And it suffocates me.

83
00:03:37,260 --> 00:03:37,820
Excuse me,

84
00:03:38,540 --> 00:03:39,380
you go ahead.

85
00:03:40,820 --> 00:03:41,860
Lu Qi is back.

86
00:03:42,860 --> 00:03:43,500
Really?

87
00:03:43,900 --> 00:03:44,660
Where is he?

88
00:03:46,460 --> 00:03:47,020
Qi,

89
00:03:47,300 --> 00:03:48,180
wait for me.

90
00:03:49,140 --> 00:03:49,740
Boss,

91
00:03:49,740 --> 00:03:51,340
you are a few years older than me,

92
00:03:51,340 --> 00:03:52,180
drop the formalities.

93
00:03:52,740 --> 00:03:53,380
Why?

94
00:03:53,660 --> 00:03:54,500
Do you think I'm old?

95
00:03:54,500 --> 00:03:55,420
Niu Qiang?

96
00:03:56,660 --> 00:03:57,540
Why is she here?

97
00:03:58,060 --> 00:03:58,660
No, no.

98
00:03:58,660 --> 00:03:59,820
I don't mean that.

99
00:04:02,460 --> 00:04:03,300
Let's talk.

100
00:04:03,660 --> 00:04:05,380
It's not impossible

101
00:04:05,380 --> 00:04:06,900
if you want to get steamy.

102
00:04:08,060 --> 00:04:08,740
Ouch!

103
00:04:11,580 --> 00:04:14,260
I broke my leg and it hurts.

104
00:04:14,260 --> 00:04:15,180
Let me tell you,

105
00:04:15,180 --> 00:04:16,340
this place is monitored.

106
00:04:16,340 --> 00:04:17,500
Don't try to blackmail me.

107
00:04:18,220 --> 00:04:19,460
I'm holding on to you now.

108
00:04:19,460 --> 00:04:21,300
Hurry, carry me to the orthopedic.

109
00:04:29,180 --> 00:04:29,580
Qi,

110
00:04:29,580 --> 00:04:30,580
do you see what this is?

111
00:04:32,940 --> 00:04:33,700
Just accept your fate,

112
00:04:33,700 --> 00:04:35,380
you won't be able to escape from me.

113
00:04:44,220 --> 00:04:44,940
Mengli,

114
00:04:45,380 --> 00:04:46,420
take two more days off

115
00:04:46,780 --> 00:04:47,540
and rest at home.

116
00:04:48,020 --> 00:04:49,420
Don't go back to work in a rush.

117
00:04:49,980 --> 00:04:50,760
I can't.

118
00:04:51,420 --> 00:04:52,300
It's less than a week

119
00:04:52,300 --> 00:04:53,860
before the men's clothing launch.

120
00:04:55,180 --> 00:04:55,860
But...

121
00:04:56,980 --> 00:04:57,860
Hold on.

122
00:05:00,940 --> 00:05:01,380
Hello.

123
00:05:02,300 --> 00:05:02,820
Grandma?

124
00:05:04,500 --> 00:05:05,220
I got it.

125
00:05:05,580 --> 00:05:06,580
I will be back at once.

126
00:05:08,940 --> 00:05:09,620
All right then.

127
00:05:10,100 --> 00:05:11,100
If it is not possible,

128
00:05:11,100 --> 00:05:12,060
you apply to the company

129
00:05:12,420 --> 00:05:13,380
to draft the design at home.

130
00:05:14,220 --> 00:05:15,020
With Niu Qiang around,

131
00:05:15,260 --> 00:05:16,180
I feel more at ease.

132
00:05:17,740 --> 00:05:18,460
Okay,

133
00:05:19,420 --> 00:05:19,860
let me try.

134
00:05:20,380 --> 00:05:20,660
Yes.

135
00:05:21,820 --> 00:05:22,780
Well, I'm leaving.

136
00:05:23,780 --> 00:05:24,180
Okay.

137
00:05:27,820 --> 00:05:28,260
Hold on.

138
00:05:35,900 --> 00:05:36,820
When you go back,

139
00:05:37,260 --> 00:05:38,900
talk to your grandma nicely.

140
00:05:39,620 --> 00:05:41,140
After all, she is the only elder
in your family.

141
00:05:42,660 --> 00:05:43,140
Sure,

142
00:05:43,620 --> 00:05:44,180
I got it.

143
00:05:53,100 --> 00:05:53,540
I'm leaving now.

144
00:05:54,300 --> 00:05:54,700
Okay.

145
00:05:56,660 --> 00:05:57,340
(Kneel!)

146
00:06:00,020 --> 00:06:01,860
For a girl from the countryside,

147
00:06:01,900 --> 00:06:04,020
how dare you use our family resources

148
00:06:04,260 --> 00:06:06,020
to suppress the Lin Group?

149
00:06:06,940 --> 00:06:07,820
If you do this,

150
00:06:08,180 --> 00:06:09,620
can you live up
to your great-grandfather,

151
00:06:09,620 --> 00:06:11,540
who worked hard
to start the business back in the day?

152
00:06:12,020 --> 00:06:13,980
Can you live up to the spirits

153
00:06:13,980 --> 00:06:15,500
of your deceased parents in heaven?

154
00:06:17,060 --> 00:06:17,780
Grandma,

155
00:06:18,140 --> 00:06:19,860
Mengli is not some girl
from the countryside.

156
00:06:20,540 --> 00:06:22,140
She is the love of my life.

157
00:06:22,780 --> 00:06:23,540
Besides,

158
00:06:23,540 --> 00:06:25,300
the Lin family is by no means kind.

159
00:06:25,300 --> 00:06:26,140
Enough!

160
00:06:26,980 --> 00:06:29,100
You are now bewitched.

161
00:06:29,780 --> 00:06:30,860
You don't even know

162
00:06:30,860 --> 00:06:32,340
what you're doing.

163
00:06:37,580 --> 00:06:38,180
Liu Mei,

164
00:06:38,900 --> 00:06:39,700
what brings you here?

165
00:06:40,100 --> 00:06:40,620
Come in.

166
00:06:42,260 --> 00:06:43,020
Mengli.

167
00:06:43,140 --> 00:06:43,420
Yes?

168
00:06:43,860 --> 00:06:44,620
I...

169
00:06:45,740 --> 00:06:46,900
I heard that you were sick.

170
00:06:47,180 --> 00:06:48,380
Yet, I was too busy with work.

171
00:06:48,380 --> 00:06:49,580
I couldn't visit you in time,

172
00:06:49,900 --> 00:06:51,100
so I asked Liu Mei to bring me here.

173
00:06:52,140 --> 00:06:52,740
Mengli,

174
00:06:53,060 --> 00:06:55,180
Director Qian came to apologize.

175
00:06:55,340 --> 00:06:57,260
Just accept his apology for my sake,

176
00:06:57,500 --> 00:06:58,220
okay?

177
00:07:01,100 --> 00:07:02,180
Let's talk about it inside.

178
00:07:12,660 --> 00:07:13,520
Mengli,

179
00:07:14,220 --> 00:07:15,540
although I am also a victim

180
00:07:16,140 --> 00:07:17,500
of Miaomiao,

181
00:07:18,140 --> 00:07:20,060
I still want to apologize in person.

182
00:07:20,780 --> 00:07:21,580
I'm sorry,

183
00:07:22,700 --> 00:07:23,900
can you forgive me?

184
00:07:25,380 --> 00:07:27,140
Don't mention it, Director Qian,

185
00:07:27,420 --> 00:07:28,460
it's too much for me to hold.

186
00:07:31,180 --> 00:07:33,300
You are still a newbie.

187
00:07:33,660 --> 00:07:36,220
The fashion design industry
is not that huge.

188
00:07:36,900 --> 00:07:38,780
We still have to
work together after this.

189
00:07:39,900 --> 00:07:41,020
Having one more friend
is always better than

190
00:07:41,620 --> 00:07:43,020
having one more enemy, right?

191
00:08:01,180 --> 00:08:07,620
♪How will you think of me then?♪

192
00:08:08,700 --> 00:08:14,300
♪Strolling the streets,
listening to our songs♪

193
